This is my VIM configure and it could run cross different platforms including
Windows and *nix. This is my first time to use github. If you love my configure or
have some questions about this configure, please feel free to contact me! Thank you!
If you want to install this configure in your computer, please run these
commands in your terminal:
1 git clone http://github.com/gmarik/vundle.git $HOME/.vim/bundle/vundle
2 git clone http://github.com/kepbod/vimrc.git $HOME/vimrc
3 cp $HOME/vimrc/.vimrc $HOME/.vimrc
4 vim .vimrc
5 :BundleInsall!
6 Just enjoy it!
PS: This configure need git support. What's more, it need lucius colorscheme,
and you can download it from
http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=2536 and install it in the right
path.

